Assumming you have emerged/installed a kernel, it in referenced to /usr/src/linux and you are currently in the /usr/src/linux directory.

== Prerequisites ==
* {{Package|dev-util/git}}
* {{Package|dev-embedded/u-boot-tools}}

{{Note|If you are using crossdev environment then replace all instances of 'make' with 'cross-make'!}}

== Configuration ==

{{Command|make omap3_pandora_defconfig}}

{{Command|make menuconfig}}

Edit accordingly!

== Compiling ==

''Kernel''
{{Command|make uImage}}

''Modules''
{{Command|make modules}}


== Installing ==

''Kernel''
{{Command|cp uImage /path/to/boot/fs}}

''Modules''
{{Command|<nowiki>make INSTALL_MOD_PATH="/path/to/lib/" modules_install</nowiki>}}

